title.rendered: Briemarpak Gamma Irradiated Alcohol Wipes, Skin Cleansing Swabs, 200 Pack

content.rendered:
These sterile (gamma irradiated) skin cleansing swabs are individually sealed single-use sachets. Each sachet contains a 2 ply / folded non woven fabric swab, saturated with BP grade 70% Isopropyl Alcohol.
Each sachet comes in an easy to tear, perforated strip of five swabs.

Sachet size: 51.4 x 46.5mm (±1mm)
Fabric size: Folded 28 x 30mm (±1mm) / Unfolded 56 x 30mm (±1mm)

  • Sterile (gamma irradiated)
  • Saturated with 70% v/v Isopropyl Alcohol
  • For external use only
  • Single use only
  • Packed as five joined with perforation
  • Sachet size: 51.4 x 46.5mm (±1mm)
  • Fabric size: 56 x 30mm (±1mm)

 

Instructions for use:
Tear open sachet, remove swab from packet and wipe, allow surface area to air dry.

  • External use only. Do not use around eyes or on irritated skin
  • Keep out of reach of children
  • Not to be taken. If swallowed, seek medical help or contact Poison Control immediately
  • Keep away from open flame
